query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(c ca hd ib) NoMergeJoin(c ca cd hd ib sr) */ select c.c_customer_id AS customer_id,
coalesce(c.c_last_name, '') || ', ' || coalesce(c.c_first_name, '') AS customername
from customer_address AS ca
inner join customer AS c
on c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk AND ca.ca_city = 'Hopewell'
inner join household_demographics AS hd
on hd.hd_demo_sk = c.c_current_hdemo_sk
inner join income_band AS ib
on ib.ib_income_band_sk = hd.hd_income_band_sk AND ib.ib_lower_bound >= 32287 AND ib.ib_upper_bound <= 32287 + 50000
inner join customer_demographics AS cd
on cd.cd_demo_sk = c.c_current_cdemo_sk
inner join store_returns AS sr
on sr.sr_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk order by c.c_customer_id LIMIT 100;
